Re-rendering a component will not cause it&#39;s state to be reseted.
Try changing your `handleSubmit` function to:
```
handleSubmit(event){
    this.props.sendMessage(this.state.message)
    this.setState({
        message:&#39;&#39;
    })
    event.preventDefault(); // So the page won&#39;t refresh
}
```

